# Local cache of the trusted Codex hotfix binary used by package-release.ps1.
# Maintainers stage `vendor-hotfix/<target-triple>/codex/codex.exe` here so the
# release packager can find it without a fresh Codex source build. The binary
# is huge (>200 MB) and must NOT be committed to git.
/vendor-hotfix/
